{"tid":1935163,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"愉景灣婚禮家族 新郎度蜜月後不適","createTime":"2020-03-20T11:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-21T02:03:07.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cebd6645583a73916643ef987d332450867f2044","tid":1935163,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"香港累計有256人確診武漢新型冠狀病毒肺炎，衛生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，第191名患者、第233名患者和第237名患者上周六（14日）曾經到愉景灣酒店參與雞尾酒會婚禮，賓客共有80多人，中心會透過新娘和新郎接觸賓客，看看是否有人出現病徵。張竹君又提到，新郎在度蜜月回港後有不適，港口衞生科正在處理，未知最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/20180633/image1584698586877.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2F20180633%2Fimage1584698586877.png&h=d57eba55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/300346/【武漢肺炎】三患者曾到愉景灣出席婚宴%E3%80%80新郎度/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F300346%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%B8%89%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E6%84%89%E6%99%AF%E7%81%A3%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E5%A9%9A%E5%AE%B4%25E3%2580%2580%E6%96%B0%E9%83%8E%E5%BA%A6%2F&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXP7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=cce7c900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/300346/【武漢肺炎】三患者曾到愉景灣出席婚宴%E3%80%80新郎度/</a>"},{"pid":"398596f3d6be1a4813a657fe4ca551d51d898761","tid":1935163,"uid":222907,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T11:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmXvnuJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmXvnuJ.jpg&h=a32c8374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4b7759c12c1dd87682b11ddc64a6de3345965a1","tid":1935163,"uid":297230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"度蜜月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3b0425405e53a190084cc75a6f784b5d243460","tid":1935163,"uid":84172